*Računa* je bila veća nego što je očekivala. (The bill was bigger than she expected.)

Ona je prebrojala *račune* i platio je sve. (She counted the bills and paid them all.)

Platna kartica je bila problem, ali onda je došla do *računa*. (The credit card was a problem, but then she got to the bill.)

Njegov *račun* je bio veći od ostale. (His bill was bigger than the others.)

Ona je izračunala *račun* i dala ga čoveku. (She calculated the bill and gave it to the man.)

On je platio *račun* i otišao. (He paid the bill and left.)